ing event and the disruption in the city.\", \"from\": 1287, \"to\": 1499, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1359, \"end\": 1373, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tony_Estanguet\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tony Estanguet\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tony_Estanguet\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tony_Estanguet\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The build-up\", \"from\": 1287, \"to\": 1299}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Games\", \"from\": 1303, \"to\": 1318}, {\"ngram\": \"many Parisians\", \"from\": 1410, \"to\": 1424}, {\"ngram\": \"the sternest critics\", \"from\": 1425, \"to\": 1445}, {\"ngram\": \"the sporting event\", \"from\": 1449, \"to\": 1467}, {\"ngram\": \"the disruption\", \"from\": 1472, \"to\": 1486}, {\"ngram\": \"the city\", \"from\": 1490, \"to\": 1498}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the wealthy districts, many families have already left for extended summer holidays, deliberately missing the July 26-Aug 11 extravaganza.\", \"from\": 1501, \"to\": 1642, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the wealthy districts\", \"from\": 1504, \"to\": 1525}, {\"ngram\": \"many families\", \"from\": 1527, \"to\": 1540}, {\"ngram\": \"extended summer holidays\", \"from\": 1563, \"to\": 1587}, {\"ngram\": \"the July 26-Aug 11 extravaganza\", \"from\": 1610, \"to\": 1641}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am following them putting up the equipment, the stadiums, the impact that it will have on us, not really the torch,\\\" student Manon Skura, 22, told AFP at the Champs-Elysees.\", \"from\": 1644, \"to\": 1820, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1772, \"end\": 1777, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Manon\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.3696398922378316e-18, \"text\": \"Manon\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Manon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Manon\"}, {\"begin\": 1794, \"end\": 1797, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agen