"from\": 1872, \"to\": 1877}, {\"ngram\": \"locations\", \"from\": 1881, \"to\": 1890}, {\"ngram\": \"the heart\", \"from\": 1894, \"to\": 1903}, {\"ngram\": \"the City\", \"from\": 1907, \"to\": 1915}, {\"ngram\": \"Light\", \"from\": 1919, \"to\": 1924}, {\"ngram\": \"temporary stadiums\", \"from\": 1931, \"to\": 1949}, {\"ngram\": \"tourist hotspots\", \"from\": 1959, \"to\": 1975}, {\"ngram\": \"the Eiffel Tower\", \"from\": 1984, \"to\": 2000}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Using the capital's fabled streets and the Seine river as a backdrop will ensure an \\\"iconic\\\" Olympics, organisers say, but it has also led to large parts of the centre being closed off and left traffic in gridlock.\", \"from\": 2039, \"to\": 2253, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2082, \"end\": 2087, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.593490144753014e-18, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the capital's fabled streets\", \"from\": 2045, \"to\": 2073}, {\"ngram\": \"a backdrop\", \"from\": 2097, \"to\": 2107}, {\"ngram\": \"an \\\"iconic\\\" Olympics\", \"from\": 2120, \"to\": 2140}, {\"ngram\": \"organisers\", \"from\": 2142, \"to\": 2152}, {\"ngram\": \"large parts\", \"from\": 2181, \"to\": 2192}, {\"ngram\": \"the centre\", \"from\": 2196, \"to\": 2206}, {\"ngram\": \"traffic\", \"from\": 2233, \"to\": 2240}, {\"ngram\": \"gridlock\", \"from\": 2244, \"to\": 2252}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The latest change to the capital's streets has been the appearance of around 44,000 metal barriers around the Seine, where a spectacular opening ceremony is being planned on July 26.\", \"from\": 2255, \"to\": 2437, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2365, \"end\": 2370, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.593490144753014e-18, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The latest change\", \"from\": 2255, \"to\": 2272}, {\"ngram\": \"the capital's streets\", \"from\": 2276, \"to\": 2297}, {\"ngram\": \"the appearance\", \"from\": 2307, \"to\": 2321}, {\"ngram\": \"around 44,000 metal barriers\", \"from\": 2325, \"to\": 2353}, {\"ngram\": \"a spectacular opening ceremony\", \"from\": 2378, \"to\": 2408}, {\"ngram\": \"July\", \"from\": 2429, \"to\": 2433}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Some residents have shared with us their amazement, as well the physical impossibility of leaving their homes,\\\" the mayor of the upmarket 6th district of Paris, Jean-Pierre Lecoq, said last week.\", \"from\": 2439, \"to\": 2635, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2594, \"end\": 2599, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.639213441223176e-22, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 2601, \"end\": 2612, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dardenne_brothers\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.1831116229466087e-15, \"text\": \"Jean-Pierre\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dardenne_brothers\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dardenne_brothers\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Some residents\", \"from\": 2440, \"to\": 2454}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 2472, \"to\": 2474}, {\"ngram\": \"their amazement\", \"from\": 2475, \"to\": 2490}, {\"ngram\": \"as well the physical impossibility\", \"from\": 2492, \"to\": 2526}, {\"ngram\": \"their homes\", \"from\": 2538, \"to\": 2549}, {\"ngram\": \"the mayor\", \"from\": 2552, \"to\": 2561}, {\"ngram\": \"the upmarket 6th district\", \"from\": 2565, \"to\": 2590}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Estanguet told AFP that pushing back the pessimists had been one of his most difficult tasks.\", \"from\": 2637, \"to\": 2730, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2652, \"end\": 2655, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\", \"score\": 0.9999998817666053, \"rank\": 1.1821901595355255e-07, \"text\": \"AFP\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Estanguet\", \"from\": 2637, \"to\": 2646}, {\"ngram\": \"the pessimists\", \"from\": 2674, \"to\": 2688}, {\"ngram\": \"his most difficult tasks\", \"from\": 2705, \"to\": 2729}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"My role has been to protect our vision against everyone who criticises, those who do not believe in it, those who would take pleasure in seeing it not go well,\\\" he said in an interview on July 11.\", \"from\": 2732, \"to\": 2929, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"My role\", \"from\": 2733, \"to\": 2740}, {\"ngram\": \"our vision\", \"from\": 2761, \"to\": 2771}, {\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 2780, \"to\": 2788}, {\"ngram\": \"pleasure\", \"from\": 2858, \"to\": 2866}, {\"ngram\": \"an interview\", \"from\": 2905, \"to\": 2917}, {\"ngram\": \"July\", \"from\": 2921, \"to\": 2925}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The torch relay had been a huge success nationally, he said, with around five million people turning out to see it since May 8.\", \"from\": 2931, \"to\": 3058, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The torch relay\", \"from\": 2931, \"to\": 2946}, {\"ngram\": \"a huge success\", \"from\": 2956, \"to\": 2970}, {\"ngram\": \"around five million people\", \"from\": 2997, \"to\": 3023}, {\"ngram\": \"May\", \"from\": 3052, \"to\": 3055}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We are delighted with how it has gone so far,\\\" he explained.\", \"from\": 3060, \"to\": 3121, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It has completely met the targets we gave ourselves.\\\"\", \"from\": 3122, \"to\": 3176, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the targets\", \"from\": 3145, \"to\": 3156}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Most importantly, the relay through 450 French towns and cities has taken place without any major security problems - testimony to the huge numbers of police officers deployed and careful planning.\", \"from\": 3178, \"to\": 3375, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3218, \"end\": 3224, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9924389521445374, \"rank\": 0.006968118361696931, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the relay\", \"from\": 3196, \"to\": 3205}, {\"ngram\": \"cities\", \"from\": 3235, \"to\": 3241}, {\"ngram\": \"place\", \"from\": 3252, \"to\": 3257}, {\"ngram\": \"any major security problems\", \"from\": 3266, \"to\": 3293}, {\"ngram\": \"testimony\", \"from\": 3296, \"to\": 3305}, {\"ngram\": \"the huge numbers\", \"from\": 3309, \"to\": 3325}, {\"ngram\": \"police officers\", \"from\": 3329, \"to\": 3344}, {\"ngram\": \"careful planning\", \"from\": 3358, \"to\": 3374}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Around 200 members of the security forces are positioned permanently around the torch, including an anti-terror Swat team and anti-drone operatives.\", \"from\": 3377, \"to\": 3525, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3489, \"end\": 3493, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Swat_District\", \"score\": 0.999999999994543, \"rank\": 5.62855133055381e-12, \"text\": \"Swat\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Swat_District\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Swat_District\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Around 200 members\", \"from\": 3377, \"to\": 3395}, {\"ngram\": \"the security forces\", \"from\": 3399, \"to\": 3418}, {\"ngram\": \"the torch\", \"from\": 3453, \"to\": 3462}, {\"ngram\": \"anti-drone operatives\", \"from\":